{"tid":131162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朝首度回應金正男遇害　形容為韓陰謀","createTime":"2017-02-23T01:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T01:49:59.000Z","uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"681a7b3b5c936b14663198b06a0c5715e1f4b3ea","tid":131162,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T01:24:26.000Z","msg":"朝首度回應金正男遇害　形容為韓陰謀<br />\n2017-02-23 HKT 08:17<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北韓首次回應領袖金正恩的兄長金正男被殺案，<span style=\"color: red;\">形容是南韓的一次「反北韓陰謀」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n北韓法律專家委員會發言人無提及金正男的名字，表示一名持外國護照的北韓公民，上星期一在馬來西亞登上航機前突然心臟休克，送院途中死亡。北韓駐大馬使館當時已表明毋須驗屍，形容大馬當局是赤裸裸侵犯北韓的國家自主權，粗暴踐踏人權的反人倫行徑。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又說，計劃派法律代表團到馬來西亞，展開具體調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金仔出招反屈「南韓」<br />\n係咪喺「屌你老母集會」學返嚟架 ?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6ab742d30031cc65fea9b06b36632f743168f1","tid":131162,"uid":79137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T01:25:51.000Z","msg":"仲唔乘機開戰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a96d6986f95f7ac32e6141dd9df3533a8e52d7","tid":131162,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肯定係跟香港公安學返黎"},{"pid":"142215a4199158db3c4a93a202043e54dbf8f9c9","tid":131162,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T01:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲唔乘機開戰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉 ,  我出 post 就係諗緊依樣野<br />\n<br />\n加上 又有另一個 POST 話  美國第七艦隊隨時 Ready"},{"pid":"1f0a04aea8d75b4618fab9d88f0631daec2acbbc","tid":131162,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"有無咁撚廢呀，敢做唔敢認，一的霸氣都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389b1777f99108ec7ffcd47f